feat: v2.0.0 - Scale & Ecosystem

PostgreSQL adapter - zero-dep via Bun.sql, 9 repository implementations,
automatic DDL migrations, config-driven adapter selection
(DATABASE_DRIVER=sqlite|postgres).

Redis cache adapter - zero-dep RESP protocol over Bun.connect() TCP,
Cache port with TTL, in-memory fallback (REDIS_ENABLED=true|false).

API versioning - URL-based /api/v1/ and /api/v2/, v2 paths normalized
to v1 for shared handlers, deprecation + sunset headers on v1.

i18n - 5 languages (en/es/fr/de/ja), 33 message keys, Accept-Language
quality-value parsing, Content-Language response header.

Kubernetes manifests - Namespace, ConfigMap, Secret, Deployment,
Service, Ingress, HPA, PDB, NetworkPolicy.

Helm chart - full chart with 8 templates.

CD pipeline - GitHub Actions: multi-arch Docker, staging + production.

E2E test suite - 28 tests with real server, complete user journey.

Load test harness - CLI-driven performance regression detection.

Postman collection - all endpoints with auto-token extraction.

Tests: 282 -> 351 (267 unit + 56 integration + 28 E2E)
